headline: Expedia (EXPE): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: What a fantastic six months it’s been for Expedia. Shares of the company have skyrocketed 71.6%, setting a new 52-week high of $289.44. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
